      <section id="id7861887">
        <title>[LO 1.1, LO 1.2, LO 1.3, LO 2.2]</title>
        <para id="id7861893">How do plants manage to not all grow in the same place and thereby avoid having to compete with each other unnecessarily?</para>
        <para id="id7861899">________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________</para>
        <figure id="id7861910">
          <media id="id7861910_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics1-2bb4.png" id="id7861910__onlineimage" height="272" width="593"/>
          </media>
        </figure>
        <figure id="id7861937">
          <media id="id7861937_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics2-b8d2.png" id="id7861937__onlineimage" height="272" width="593"/>
